public class NCLBindParam<T extends NCLElement,Ec extends NCLConnectorParam,R extends ExternalReferenceType>
extends NCLParam<T,Ec,R>

Class that represents a bind parameter element. This element is used to define a value to a parameter defined in a connector.
This element defines the attributes:

  • name - reference to the name of the parameter defined by a connector. This attribute is required.
  • value - value of the parameter defined by a connector. This attribute is required.
